# ==============================================================================
# Rust / Cargo Build Artifacts
# ==============================================================================
/target/
/debug/

# Rustfmt backup files and compiler crash dumps
**/*.rs.bk
rustc-ice-*.txt

# MSVC Windows debugging files
*.pdb

# ==============================================================================
# General Dotfile Blanket Rule
# ==============================================================================
# Ignore all files and directories starting with a dot.
.*

# --- EXCEPTIONS (Do NOT ignore these) ---
# Negate the blanket ignore above for directories and configurations essential
# for team collaboration and repository workflows.
!.git/            # CRUCIAL: Prevents CI and copy tools from skipping the .git folder
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!.editorconfig
!.github/
!.cargo/


# ==============================================================================
# Secrets & Credentials (Safety Net)
# ==============================================================================
# Additional safety rules to catch credentials that might not start with a dot.
.env*
*.pem
*.key
secrets.json
certificates/

# ==============================================================================
# Other Common Ignored Files
# ==============================================================================
AGENTS.md
